---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="Grant Holle">
  <main class="relative z-0 flex py-6 md:items-center justify-center min-h-screen px-4 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto w-full relative z-0">
      <Card>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold permanent-marker">Yo.</h1>
        <p>My name is Grant. I love building software for the web, among other things.</p>
        <p>I've lived abroad for the last 9 years (7 in China, 2 in the UAE), but have recently made my way back to the US.</p>
        <p>I'm building <a href="https://www.archboard.io" target="_blank">Archboard</a>, an open source company whose applications make things easier for schools. I'm also helping build <a href="https://app.teachrn.com" target="_blank">TeachRN</a>, a nurse mentorship marketplace.</p>
        <p>Check out my <a href="https://github.com/grantholle" target="_blank">GitHub</a> to view my recent activity on public repositories or connect on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/grant-holle/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>.</p>
        <p>Here are a few projects I'm proud of:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-8">
          <li><a href="https://github.com/grantholle/moviedb-promise" target="_blank">moviedb-promise</a>, a TypeScript API wrapper for themoviedb.org.</li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/grantholle/laravel-timezone" target="_blank">laravel-timezone</a>, a Laravel package with some helpful timezone tools.</li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/grantholle/laravel-powerschool-auth" target="_blank">laravel-powerschool-auth</a>, a Laravel package to use with PowerSchool authentication.</li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/grantholle/powerschool-api" target="_blank">powerschool-api</a>, an API wrapper and tool for PowerSchool's API.</li>
        </ul>
      </Card>
    </div>

    <div id="wrapper" class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 pr-4 z-10 translate-y-[92%] lg:hover:translate-y-[80%] transition ease-in-out duration-150">
      <div id="bubble" class="invisible opacity-0 transition duration-250 bg-white w-[325px] rounded px-6 py-10 border-4 border-black text-center absolute -top-[165px] -left-[160px] text-4xl -rotate-6 permanent-marker">
        <blockquote class="">You knowâ€¦ We're living in a society!</blockquote>
      </div>
      <button class="relative z-10 block active:outline-none" id="george">
        <span class="sr-only">Show George Costanza</span>
        <img src="/society.webp" alt="George Costanza" />
      </button>
    </div>
    <div id="backdrop" class="invisible transition ease-in-out duration-200 opacity-0 fixed z-0 inset-0 bg-cyan-400/50 backdrop-filter backdrop-blur-md px-2 h-screen"></div>
  </main>
</Layout>

